This Python script allows you to:
- Scrape Billboard's Hot 100 chart for any given date
- Authenticate with Spotify using OAuth
- Create a private Spotify playlist with the top 100 songs from your chosen date
- Handle missing tracks and alternative versions automatically

Perfect for creating nostalgic playlists or exploring music history!

